              <text x="86" y="272" font-size="16">Test prędkości: bez VPN → z VPN (blisko) → z VPN (kraj)</text>

              <rect x="540" y="214" width="380" height="92" rx="16" fill="#fee2e2" stroke="#000" stroke-width="3"></rect>
